skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fun recipes
des: Fun Recipes is a skill to help you to cook your daily meal with step by step instructions. You can search recipes by meal type and also by ingredients. Fun Recipes will guide you through the cooking process with easy instructions. You can also save your favorite recipes for fast search.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
